data.description: Discover the perfect single- family property on a quiet cul-de-sac in the highly demanded community of the Dominion walk subdivision. This charming property features a fenced backyard for outdoor enjoyment as well as exclusive access to the community pool and tennis court. It’s only a mile away from Brookwood High school, ensuring an easy commute to school. Plus, with a recently replaced roof that is only two years old, it relieves the worry of Maintenance. Don’t miss your chance to make this forever home-it won't last long.
